nodes.text: Bogey 9662 was a clone trooper and member of Bogey Squad during the Great Jedi Purge on Kashyyyk. He wore the armor of a clone scout trooper.

Under Clone Commander Faie, Bogey 9662 and his squad hunted down the Jedi Master Quinlan Vos who survived the initial Order 66 attack. While approaching the injured Jedi, 9662 was killed by a tree trap, which hung and choked him. The trap was designed by the Wookiee Chak.
